riant-emoji: normal; font-weight: 500; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; border-top: none; padding: 10px 16px; text-align: left;">Página</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td style="border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; min-width: 100px; max-width: min(30vw, 320px); padding: 10px 16px 10px 0px;"><span style="font-weight: 600;">1- INFORMAÇÕES BÁSICAS</span></td><td style="border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; min-width: 100px; max-width: min(30vw, 320px); padding: 10px 16px;"></td><td style="border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; min-width: 100px; max-width: min(30vw, 320px); padding: 10px 0px 10px 16px;"></td></tr><tr><td style="border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; min-width: 100px; max-width: min(30vw, 320px); padding: 10px 16px 10px 0px;">Órgão e Cidade Licitante:</td><td style="border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; min-width: 100px; max-width: min(30vw, 320px); padding: 10px 16px;">Prefeitura Municipal de Riachinho - TO, através do Fundo Municipal de Saúde de Riachinho.</td><td style="border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; min-width: 100px; max-width: min(30vw, 320px); padding: 10px 0px 10px 16px;">1, 3</td></tr><tr><td style="border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; min-width: 100px; max-width: min(30vw, 320px); padding: 10px 16px 10px 0px;">Modalidade:</td><td style="border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; min-width: 100px; max-width: min(30vw, 320px); padding: 10px 16px;">Credenciamento Eletrônico.</td><td style="border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; min-width: 100px; max-width: min(30vw, 320px); padding: 10px 0px 10px 16px;">1, 3</td></tr><tr><td style="border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; min-width: 100px; max-width: min(30vw, 320px); padding: 10px 16px 10px 0px;">Habitantes da cidade Licitante (BUSCAR EXTERNAMENTE):</td><td style="border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; min-width: 100px; max-width: min(30vw, 320px); padding: 10px 16px;">[Dado a ser consultado externamente. Com base em dados do IBGE, Riachinho/TO tinha aproximadamente 4.400 habitantes em 2022.]</td><td style="border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; min-width: 100px; max-width: min(30vw, 320px); padding: 10px 0px 10px 16px;">-</td></tr><tr><td style="border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; min-width: 100px; max-width: min(30vw, 320px); padding: 10px 16px 10px 0px;">Onde será executado o serviço?</td><td style="border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; min-width: 100px; max-width: min(30vw, 320px); padding: 10px 16px;">Município de Riachinho/TO. O serviço (teleconsulta) será prestado remotamente, mas o beneficiário final é a população do município.</td><td style="border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; min-width: 100px; max-width: min(30vw, 320px); padding: 10px 0px 10px 16px;">2, 15</td></tr><tr><td style="border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; min-width: 100px; max-width: min(30vw, 320px); padding: 10px 16px 10px 0px;">O licitante deve dar o local de execução?</td><td style="border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; min-width: 100px; max-width: min(30vw, 320px); padding: 10px 16px;">Sim. A empresa deve prestar os serviços ao Município de Riachinho/TO. O atendimento é via telemedicina, mas a demanda e a gestão são locais.</td><td style="border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; min-width: 100px; max-width: min(30vw, 320px); padding: 10px 0px 10px 16px;">19 (§1º)</td></tr><tr><td style="border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; min-width: 100px; max-width: min(30vw, 320px); padding: 10px 16px 10px 0px;">Qual é a distância até o local de execução (capital ou cidade com mais de 150 mil habitantes) em km e em horas? (BUSCAR EXTERNAMENTE)</td><td style="border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; min-width: 100px; max-width: min(30vw, 320px); padding: 10px 16px;">[Dado a ser consultado externamente. Riachinho está a aproximadamente 430 km de Palmas (capital) e a cerca de 300 km de Araguaína (população &gt;150k). As viagens levam em média 5h e 4h, respectivamente.]</td><td style="border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; min-width: 100px; max-width: min(30vw, 320px); padding: 10px 0px 10px 16px;">-</td></tr><tr><td style="border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; min-width: 100px; max-width: min(30vw, 320px); padding: 10px 16px 10px 0px;">O edital é regido por alguma legislação específica (Lei 14.133/21, Decreto, etc.)?</td><td style="border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; min-width: 100px; max-width: min(30vw, 320px); padding: 10px 16px;">Sim. Lei nº 14.133/2021 (Nova Lei de Licitações) e Decreto nº 11.878/2024.</td><td style="border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; min-width: 100px; max-width: min(30vw, 320px); padding: 10px 0px 10px 16px;">3, 16, 18</td></tr><tr><td style="border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; min-width: 100px; max-width: min(30vw, 320px); padding: 10px 16px 10px 0px;"><span style="font-weight: 600;">2- OBJETO E CRONOGRAMA</span></td><td style="border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; min-width: 100px; max-width: min(30vw, 320px); padding: 10px 16px;"></td><td style="border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; min-width: 100px; max-width: min(30vw, 320px); padding: 10px 0px 10px 16px;"></td></tr><tr><td style="border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; min-width: 100px; max-width: min(30vw, 320px); padding: 10px 16px 10px 0px;">Objeto:</td><td style="border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; min-width: 100px; max-width: min(30vw, 320px); padding: 10px 16px;">Credenciamento para contratação de empresa especializada em prestação de serviços médicos (clínico geral e especialistas) via telemedicina.</td><td style="border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; min-width: 100px; max-width: min(30vw, 320px); padding: 10px 0px 10px 16px;">1, 3, 15</td></tr><tr><td style="border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; min-width: 100px; max-width: min(30vw, 320px); padding: 10px 16px 10px 0px;">Data limite para cadastro/envio da proposta?</td><td style="border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; min-width: 100px; max-width: min(30vw, 320px); padding: 10px 16px;">Período de apresentação das propostas e documentações:&nbsp;<span style="font-weight: 600;">DE 18/12/2025 A 12/01/2026</span>.</td><td style="border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; min-width: 100px; max-width: min(30vw, 320px); padding: 10px 0px 10px 16px;">1</td></tr><tr><td style="border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; min-width: 100px; max-width: min(30vw, 320px); padding: 10px 16px 10px 0px;">Data prevista para a disputa?</td><td style="border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; min-width: 100px; max-width: min(30vw, 320px); padding: 10px 16px;">Não especificada no corpo do edital. A modalidade é credenciamento, não havendo "sessão de disputa" tradicional. A disputa se dá pela habilitação e posterior ordem de contratação.</td><td style="border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; min-width: 100px; max-width: min(30vw, 320px); padding: 10px 0px 10px 16px;">-</td></tr><tr><td style="border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; min-width: 100px; max-width: min(30vw, 320px); padding: 10px 16px 10px 0px;">Qual a data limite para esclarecimentos e impugnações?</td><td style="border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; min-width: 100px; max-width: min(30vw, 320px); padding: 10px 16px;">Não há prazo final explícito. Impugnações e pedidos de esclarecimento podem ser feitos enquanto o edital permanecer em vigor (15 dias úteis a partir da publicação).</td><td style="border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; min-width: 100px; max-width: min(30vw, 320px); padding: 10px 0px 10px 16px;">10 (item 7.1)</td></tr><tr><td style="border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; min-width: 100px; max-width: min(30vw, 320px); padding: 10px 16px 10px 0px;">Qual é o portal ou local da sessão?</td><td style="border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); font-variant-nu