,25</span><br style="line-height: 1.8; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Poppins, Helvetica, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; background-color: rgb(248, 249, 250);"><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Poppins, Helvetica, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; background-color: rgb(248, 249, 250);">* Polissonografia (Basal): ~48,75</span><br style="line-height: 1.8; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Poppins, Helvetica, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; background-color: rgb(248, 249, 250);"><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Poppins, Helvetica, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; background-color: rgb(248, 249, 250);">* Polissonografia (Titulação de CPAP): ~46,67</span><br style="line-height: 1.8; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Poppins, Helvetica, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; background-color: rgb(248, 249, 250);"><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Poppins, Helvetica, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; background-color: rgb(248, 249, 250);">* Broncoprovocação: ~47,92</span><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Poppins, Helvetica, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; background-color: rgb(248, 249, 250);"></span></p><p><br></p>PORTAL – Sistema iConsórcio (https://cisnap.nuvemsitcon.com.br/cisnap)  <br>
